text: Shakir Shikhaliyev (born 19 November 1990) is an Azerbaijani gymnast. He competed in six events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Azerbaijani male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Azerbaijan Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Baku
